quran[399]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Inna: \"anwa ay d awal nnwen, a yimceggâan"
  51,32,"Nnan: \"nekwni neppuceggaâ d ar ugdud ibe$wviyen"
  51,33,Iwakken a ten neôoem s uéôu n talaxt
  51,34,i ipwaôecmen s$uô Mass ik i ucmiten
  51,35,"Nessuffe$ kra illan, degs, n lmumnin"
  51,36,"Nufa kan degs, yiwen uxxam n imvuâen"
  51,37,Neooa p id d assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb aqeôêan
  51,38,"I di Musa, mi t id Nuzen i Ferâun, s udabu n ûûeê"
  51,39,"Iaâûa, akked imalalen is, inna: \"d aseêêar, ne$ d aôehbani"
  51,40,"Neddem it, neppa akked iâsekriwen is, Nveggeô iten ar yill. Tiyta degs"
  51,41,"I di Âad, mi sen Nuzen avu asexvi"
  51,42,"Ur ippaooa ayen immuger, alamma irra t am rrmim"
  51,43,"I Tamud, mi pwanecden: \"siwa tallit ara tezhum"
  51,44,"Âuûan lameô n Mass nnsen. Tewwet iten id ssiâqa, nitni la pwalin"
  51,45,"Ur zmiren a d kren, ur pwasellken"
  51,46,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel, llan, s tidep, d agdud iballa$en"
  51,47,"Igenni, Nebna t s loehd, d Nekwni it Issewsaân"
  51,48,"Tamurt, Nessa p. Ay gerzen Wid Itessun"
  51,49,"Di yal cci, Nexleq tayuga, ahat a d tesmektim"
  51,50,"Ihi, srifget ar Öebbi. Nek, ih, s$uôeS ar $uôwen, d aneddaô ipbegginen"
  51,51,"Ur sâut, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven! Nek, ih, s$uôeS ar $uôwen, d aneddaô ipbegginen"
  51,52,"Akka, ur iusi umazan ar wid i ten id izwaren, mebla ma nnan as: \"d aseêêar ne$ d aôehbani"
  51,53,"Day ppuweûûan $ef waya? Xaîi, nitni d agdud izegren tilas"
  51,54,Ïîixxeô asen; ur deg k tiyta
  51,55,"Smektay ed. Asmekti, s tidep, infaâ lmumnin"
  51,56,"Xelqe$ leonun akked imdanen, iwakken kan ad iyI âabden"
  51,57,"Ur b$i$ segsen ôôeéq, ur b$i$ ad iyi cceççen"
  51,58,"Öebbi, s tidep, d Aôeééaq, d Bu tezmert n ûûeê"
  51,59,"Ih, i wid idensen, amur am umur imeddukwal nnsen. Ulay$eô iyI $eûben"
  51,60,"A tawa$it n wid ijehlen, ilmend n wass i sen ippuwaââden"
  52,1,S udrar
  52,2,S Tezmamt ippujerrden
  52,3,di lka$ev ivelqen
  52,4,S texxamt iâamôen
  52,5,S tseddarit aâlayen
  52,6,S yill icebbwlen
  52,7,"Aâaqeb n Mass ik, s tidep, ad ivôu"
  52,8,Ur isâi ara t sfunngen
  52,9,"Ass ideg ara imbwiwel igenni, d ambwiwel"
  52,10,"Ad lêun idurar, d tikli"
  52,11,"A ssexv, assen, n wid iskiddiben"
  52,12,Wid inexôen deg uraren
  52,13,"Ass ideg ara pwaveggôen ar tmes n Loahennama, d aveggeô"
  52,14,Apan tmes nni i la tnekôem
  52,15,"D ssêur waya, ne$ d kunwi ur nwala ara"
  52,16,"Kecmet ep. Iâuva fellawen, tûebôem, ne$ ur teûbiôem. A ppeppuqeîîim kan $ef wayen txeddmem"
  52,17,"Wanag wid ipêezziben, di leonanat, akked zzhu"
  52,18,"Feôêen s wayen i sen Ifka Mass nnsen. Isellek iten, Mass nnsen, seg uâaqeb ujajiê"
  52,19,"àçet, teswem, di lehna, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  52,20,"èélen af imîeôêen, d idurra; d tiêuôiyin lâin ukud iten Njewweo"
  52,21,"Wid iumnen, u âanden ten, warraw nnsen, ar liman nnsen, a ten Nessemlil akked warraw nnsen. Ur Nessenqas acemma seg igiten nnsen. Yal amdan ad immager ayen ikseb"
  52,22,Ad asen d Nefk izwayen akked uksum seg wayen cedhan
  52,23,"Dinna ad ppemyeppaken lkas, ideg ur illi usîeômel, ne$ ssebba n tuccva"
  52,24,"Garasen, ddewiôen ilmeéiyen i nitni, amzun d tiyaqutin mesîuôen"
  52,25,"Zzin, kra $er kra, pmesteqsayen"
  52,26,"Nnan d: \"ni$ nella, zik, di twacult nne$, nugad"
  52,27,"I$at a$ Öebbi, Isellek a$ seg ujajiê n tmes"
  52,28,"Ni$ nella, zik, nepnuju $uôeS. Neppa, s tidep, d A$eyyat Ipêunun"
  52,29,"Ihi, ccfu ar keçç, s l$it n Mass ik, ur telliv d agezzan, ne$ d aôehbani"
  52,30,"Ne$, ad inin: \"d amedyaz. A naôou asali s akud"
  52,31,"Ini: \"gganit! Nek, yidwen, seg wid ipganin"
  52,32,"Ne$ d tirga nnsen i sen iumôen aya, ne$ nitni d agdud izegren tilas"
  52,33,"Ne$ ad inin: \"isnulfa t id\". Xaîi! Ur uminen"
  52,34,"Ihi, a d awin ameslay i t icban, ma d tidep ay ssawalen"
  52,35,"Ne$ pwaxelqen seg ulac, ne$ d nitni ay d ixellaqen"
  52,36,"Ne$ xelqen tamurt akked igenwan? Xaîi, ur pputebbten"
  52,37,"Ne$ $uôsen lexzayen n Mass ik, ne$ nitni d imvebbôen"
  52,38,"Ne$ sâan sellum ad ssemêessen, segs. Ihi, win islan segsen, a d iawi adabu n ûûeê"
  52,39,"Ne$ i Neppa tullas, i kunwi arrac"
  52,40,"Ne$ tessutrev asen taqdiât, fellasen d îîlaba ééayen"
  52,41,"Ne$ $uôsen tabavnit, d$a la pparun"
  52,42,Ne$ b$an ad andin? D wid ijehlen ara ipwaîîfen
  52,43,"Ne$ sâan ôebbi, ur Nelli d Öebbi? Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen pcaraken"
  52,44,"Lemmer ad walin amur igenni i$li, ad as inin: \"d asigna i izdin"
  52,45,"Ihi, eoo iten, ard mlilen d wass n ssiâqa nnsen"
  52,46,"Ass, ideg ur asen d teppawi acemma, tandit nnsen; ur asen illi usettaô"
  52,47,"I wid idensen, s tidep, aâaqeb nniven, maca tegwti degsen, ur éôin"
  52,48,"Eûbeô i wayen d Iêudd Mass ik, aql ak, s tidep, ger wallen nne£. Sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, mara d tekkrev"
  52,49,"Sbuccaâ iT deg iv, u mara xsin yitran"
  53,1,S yitri mara ixeppi
  53,2,"Ur innetlaf, ur i$liv umeddakwel nnwen"
  53,3,Ur d iqqaô akken i s ihwan
  53,4,"D aweêêi kan, id ippuweêêan"
  53,5,Islemd it bab n tezmert iqwan
  53,6,D bab n tezmert irs ed
  53,7,u neppa di lejba aâlayen
  53,8,"Sinna iqeôb ed, ippucengel"
  53,9,"atan tasurift n sin ixtucen, ne$ ur tebbwiv"
  53,10,"D$a iweêêa i umdan iS, ayen iweêêa"
  53,11,Ur iskaddeb wul deg wayen iwala
  53,12,"Day a t tnaqwmem, $ef wayen iwala"
  53,13,Ni$ iéôa t di trusi s nniven
  53,14,ar tedxwent n talast
  53,15,u$uô illa leonan usemlili
  53,16,Mi tesbur tedxwent ta$wlaft
  53,17,"ur iwweônenni yiéôi, ur izgir"
  53,18,"Ni$ iwala kra issekniyen imeqwôaêanen, n Mass is"
  53,19,Twalam Allat akked Lâuzza
  53,20,"Akked Manat, tis krav nniven"
  53,21,"Day i kunwi ddkeô, i Neppa nnta"
  53,22,"Wagi, ihi, d beîîu aneêyaf"
  53,23,"Wigi d ismawen kan i sent tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur sent d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya, akked wayen cehwant teôwiêin. Ni$ tusa ten id nnhaya s$uô Mass nnsen"
  53,24,"Aâni, i umdan, ayen issaram"
  53,25,"Tamezwarut akked tneggarut, n Öebbi"
  53,26,"Acêal n lmalayek deg igenwan, ur d teppawi acemma ccafuâa nnsent, siwa deffir tsriê n Öebbi, $ef win Ib$a u Iôuva"
  53,27,"Ih, wid ur numin ara di laxeôt, ppaken i lmalayek ismawen n nnta"
  53,28,Ur sâin fellas kra n tmusni. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya. Wanag nnwaya ur tebbwi acemma si tidep
  53,29,"Ihi, eoo win iwexxôen i usmekti nne£, i ib$an kan tudert n ddunit"
  53,30,"D aya ay sen tefka tmusni. Mass ik, war ccekk, Iéôa sennig akw, anwa innetlafen seg ubrid iS; Iéôa sennig akw, anwa i ipwanhan"
  53,31,"N Öebbi ayen akw illan deg igenwan, illan di tmurt. Ad Iqeîîi wid ifalîan $ef wayen xedmen, ad Ioazi wid issweqmen, s ûûam"
  53,32,"Wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen akked tucmitin, siwa lfalîat fessusen, ihi, d uwsiâ ssmaê n Mass ik. Neppa Issen ikwen sennig akw, mi kwen id Ixleq seg wakal, mi tellam d icelleqluqen, deg iâabbav n tyimmatin nnwen. Ur staâmilet tezdeg deg iman nnwen! Neppa Iéôa sennig akw, anwa iêezzben"
  53,33,Twalav win iwexxôen
  53,34,"i ifkan cwiî, iccuêen"
  53,35,"Day isâa tamusni n tbavnit, d$a iwala"
  53,36,Ne$ ur ippuxebbeô $ef tewôiqin n Musa
  53,37,Akked Ibôahim ineûêen
  53,38,Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev
  53,39,"I umdan, siwa ayen inki"
  53,40,Ankay is a t iwali
  53,41,"Sinna, a t Ikafi s lufa"
  53,42,"Ih, ar Mass ik, taggara"
  53,43,"D Neppa i Issevûan, i Issruyen"
  53,44,"D Neppa i Ineqqen, i Issidiren"
  53,45,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tayuga, ddkeô akked nnta"
  53,46,Si tiqqit n l$ella ma tuzzel
  53,47,"FellaS, axlaq nniven"
  53,48,"D Neppa i I$ennun, i Iqenâan"
  53,49,D Neppa i d Mass n Ciâra
  53,50,D Neppa i Isnegren Âad imezwura
  53,51,"Si Tamud, ur d Iooi ara"
  53,52,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, war ccekk, iugar iten ddens, lbbwe$v"
  53,53,Issenger tid inneqlaben
  53,54,Idel iten s wayen idellen
  53,55,Anta talalt n Mass ik ara tnamerev
  53,56,Wagi d aneddaô seg ineddaôen n zik
  53,57,A d taéé tin d ippaééen
  53,58,"War Öebbi, ur illi ara p id issdehôen"
  53,59,Iswehm ikwen wawal a
  53,60,La tdessem ur la tepprum
  53,61,Kunwi di zzhu
  53,62,"Knut i Öebbi, âabdet"
  54,1,Iqeôb ed yimir; ifelleq waggur
  54,2,"Ma walan assekni, ad wexxôen, ad inin: \"ipkemmil ssêur"
  54,3,"Nekôen, îîafaôen lemcihwat nnsen. Ad iûaô yal lameô"
  54,4,"Ni$ usan ten id kra isallen, u wayen degsen iswexxiôen"
  54,5,Üûwab issakwayen. Maca ula iwumi aâaggen
  54,6,"Ihi, îîixxeô asen! Asmi ara d isiwel, uberraê, ar wayen iwaâôen"
  54,7,"s wallen ibran, ara d ff$en si tneîlin, am ujôad iwezzâen"
  54,8,"Ad éedmen, âaooôen, ar uberraê, ad inin ijehliyen: \"wagi d ass uwâiô"
  54,9,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, iskaddeb. Skaddben amdan nne$. Nnan: \"d aôehbani\". Rran t id"
  54,10,"Inuj ar Mass is: \"nek pwa$elbe$, Awes"
  54,11,"Nelli tibbura igenni, i waman d ihedman"
  54,12,"Nesgguffaâ d laânaûeô n tmurt, mlalen waman akken ipwagzem lameô"
  54,13,"Nebbwi t af tencirin, akked tavuî n tiffest"
  54,14,"Teppeddu zdat wallen nne£, d arraz i win ipwanekôen"
  54,15,Ni$ Neooa p id d assekni. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,16,Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,17,Ni$ Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,18,Âad skaddben. Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,19,"Ih, Nuzen asen aûeôûaô, ass amekêus, imezgi"
  54,20,Ippawi medden amzun d iqeôôumen n tezdayin ipwaqelâen
  54,21,Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,22,Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,23,Tamud skaddben aâeggen
  54,24,"Nnan: \"day a neddu d yiwen n umdan segne$? Ihi, nekwni, war ccekk, di ttelfan, akked tisselbi"
  54,25,"Day d neppa, garane$, u$uô id iusa uneddeô? Wanag neppa, d akeddab uqbiê"
  54,26,"Ad walin azekka, anwa ay d akeddab uqbiê"
  54,27,"A Nazen, ih, tal$wemt i ujeôôeb nnsen. Qaôaâ ten, ili k d aûebôi"
  54,28,Xebbeô iten ar aman ad pwafeôqen. Mkul tissit s tidwelt
  54,29,"Ssawlen i umeddakwel nnsen. Iusa d, igezm as ivaôen"
  54,30,Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,31,"Nuzen asen d, s tidep, yiwen usu$u. U$alen am alim di tbergent"
  54,32,Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,33,Agdud n Luî skaddben aâeggen
  54,34,"Ihi, Nuzen asen ajebwani, kkes ed tawacult n Luî, i Nsellek qbel tafara"
  54,35,d l$it s$uône£. Akka ay Nepkafi wid isnemmiren
  54,36,"Ni$ iâaggen asen, Newâaô. Rran aâeggen di ccekk"
  54,37,"Ni$ ssutren t $ef inebgawen is. Nesder$el allen nnsen: \"jeôôbet aâaqeb iW, akked uâaggen iW"
  54,38,"Iusa ten id, ssbeê zik, uâaqeb imezgi"
  54,39,"Jeôôbet aâaqeb iW, akked uâeggen iW"
  54,40,Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,41,Ni$ iusa n uâeggen ar twacult n Ferâun
  54,42,"Skaddben issekniyen nne£, meôôa. Naâtad iten s ufus ioehden, izemren"
  54,43,Aâni ijehliyen nnwen ifen wigi? Ne$ tesâam laânaya deg Ihellilen
  54,44,"Ne$ a d inin: \"nekwni d agraw ara irebêen"
  54,45,"Agraw ad ixseô, ad wexxôen"
  54,46,"Ih, imir d ppaâud nnsen. Imir d lhejna, u ôéag kteô"
  54,47,"Ih, ibe$wdiyen di ttelfan akked tisselbi"
  54,48,"Asmi ara kkerkren ar tmes, $ef udmawen nnsen: \"jeôôbet tanalit ujajiê"
  54,49,"Ih, yal cci, Nxelq it s lmizan"
  54,50,"Lameô nne£ siwa yiwen, am unqej n tiî"
  54,51,Ni$ Nesqucc wid i kwen icban. Day llan wid ara d ismektin
  54,52,Yal igi nnsen deg Ihellilen
  54,53,"Akw, meééi meqqweô, ppujerrden"
  54,54,"Wid ipêezziben, s tidep, di leonanat akked isaffen"
  54,55,"deg umekkan n tidep, ar Ugellid Uzmir"
  55,1,Aênin
  55,2,Isseêfev Leqwôan
  55,3,Ixleq amdan
  55,4,Isselmed as ôôkuz
  55,5,"Iîij akked waggur, s leêsab"
  55,6,"Itran akked ttjuô, knan"
  55,7,"Igenni, Issuli t; Issers ed lmizan"
  55,8,Ur xedâat di lmizan
  55,9,"Weznet s tidep, ur ssexsaôet lmizan"
  55,10,Issewsaâ tamurt i imexlaq
  55,11,"Degs izwayen, tizdayin sut tkummiwin"
  55,12,"iâqqayen s usa$uô, iferrawen utebtil"
  55,13,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,14,"Ixleq amdan si talaxt, am ujeqduô"
  55,15,Ixleq loenn seg ujajiê n tmessi
  55,16,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,17,"Mass n sin igmav, Mass n sin ituram"
  55,18,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,19,Iooa sin ilellen ad mqaôaben
  55,20,"Garasen agadir, ur zegren"
  55,21,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,22,"Teff$ent ed, segsen, tyuqat akked lmeôoan"
  55,23,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,24,"IneS lembwabeô pwabnan di yill, am idurar"
  55,25,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,26,Ad ifut degs kra illan
  55,27,"A d igwri udem n Mass ik, Bab n ccan akked cciâa"
  55,28,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,29,"Teppren T, yal ass, kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan, Neppa la Ixelleq"
  55,30,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,31,"A d Nelhi yidwen, a sin iéayanen"
  55,32,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,33,"A yagraw n leonun akked imdanen, ma tzemrem a pzegrem akin i tmurt akked igenwan, zegret! Ur tepzeggirem siwa ma s udabu"
  55,34,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,35,A d teppewwtem s ijujaê n tmes akked nnêas. Ur tepsellikem iman nnwen
  55,36,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,37,"Ma ifelleq igenni, iu$al d azeggwa$ am u$eggwad"
  55,38,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,39,"assen, amdan ne$ loenn, ur fellas asteqsi $ef ubekkav is"
  55,40,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,41,"Ibe$wviyen, a d banen ar ccwami nnsen. Ad pwaîîfen seg icebbuben akked ivaôen"
  55,42,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,43,D tagi ay d Loahennama i skaddben ibe$wviyen
  55,44,Ad ddewwiôen garas akked wayen ippayzagen
  55,45,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,46,"I win iugaden ibeddi zdat Mass is, sin leonanat"
  55,47,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,48,"S tzegzew, d imselîen"
  55,49,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,50,Degs sin i$bula pfeggiven
  55,51,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,52,"Degs yal izwayen, d tiyugiwin"
  55,53,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,54,èélen af imîeôêen ippuêewcen; izwayen n sin leonanat wâan asen
  55,55,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,56,"Dinna, sut usekkud ipsetêin, ur tent innul yiwen, uqbel nnsen, d loenn ne$ d amdan"
  55,57,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,58,Amzun nitenti d lyaqut akked lmeôoan
  55,59,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,60,"Nni$ arraz n wayen ilhan, d ayen ilhan"
  55,61,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,62,Sin leonanat nniven
  55,63,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,64,S tzegzewt isemmxen
  55,65,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,66,Degsen snat n tliwa gguffant
  55,67,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,68,"Degsen izwayen, tizdayin, ôemman"
  55,69,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,70,Degsen tiferni akked ûûam
  55,71,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,72,Tiêuôiyin ized$en di texxamin
  55,73,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,74,"Ur tent innul yiwen, uqbel nnsen, d loenn ne$ d amdan"
  55,75,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,76,Ad élen af imîeôêen izegzawen akked d tôakniwin ilhan
  55,77,"Anwa seg i$iten n Mass nnwen ara teskiddben, i sin"
  55,78,"Iôqa ism n Mass ik, Bab n ccan akked cciâa"
  56,1,"Mara d tas, tin ara d iasen"
  56,2,"ef tisin is, ur illi ucehrir"
  56,3,"Tessrusu, treffed"
  56,4,"Ma tenhez tmurt, lhezz iqesêen"
  56,5,idurar ftutsen
  56,6,u$alen d a$ebbaô ippuwezzâen
  56,7,a d tevêum krav leûnaf
  56,8,"at uyeffus. At uyeffus, anwi ten"
  56,9,"At uzelmav. At uzelmav, anwi ten"
  56,10,"Akked imezwura, imezwura"
  56,11,Widak d iqôiben
  56,12,di leonanat isaâdiyen
  56,13,"Seg imenza, deg waîas idsen"
  56,14,"Seg ineggura, drus nnsen"
  56,15,£ef imîeôêen iévan
  56,16,"éélen fellasen, mqabalen"
  56,17,Tezzin asen ilmeéiyen iwekkôen
  56,18,"s tbuqalin, iqbucen, akked lkas n tissit iûfan"
  56,19,"Yis, ur ppavnen, ur sekkôen"
  56,20,"Izwayen, seg wid smenyafen"
  56,21,"Aksum n yifôax, seg win cedhan"
  56,22,Tiêuôiyin lâin
  56,23,am tyaqutin iffren
  56,24,D arraz n wayen xeddmen
  56,25,"Ur din sellen awal n leqbaêa, ne$ n tuccva"
  56,26,"siwa awal n tifrat, tifrat"
  56,27,"At uyeffus, at uyeffus, d acu ten"
  56,28,"Ar tzegwart, war isennanen"
  56,29,Tulmatin iurwen
  56,30,Tili iwsâen
  56,31,Aman ippazalen
  56,32,Aîas n yizwayen
  56,33,"ur zegzawit, ur ppugedlen"
  56,34,Imîeôêen aâlayen
  56,35,D Nekwni itent Ixelqen
  56,36,Nerra tent d tiêuôiyin
  56,37,"pêemmilent, d tizyiwin"
  56,38,i at uyeffus
  56,39,"Seg imenza, deg aîas idsen"
  56,40,"Seg ineggura, deg aîas idsen"
  56,41,"At uzelmav, at uzelmav, d acu ten"
  56,42,"Deg wavu, akked waman iô$an"
  56,43,Tili n wabbu iô$an
  56,44,"Ur degs tasmuvi, lekyasa"
  56,45,"Ih, nitni zik, llan ôwan"
  56,46,Zgan deg ubekkav abarar
  56,47,"Llan qqaôen: \"ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, akked i$san, day a d a$ d rren"
  56,48,Akked imezwura nne$ imenza
  56,49,"Ini: \"ih, imezwura akked ineggura"
  56,50,ad ppujemmlen ar temlilit n wass ipwassnen
  56,51,"D$a, ih, a yim$eôôqen, i illan d inekkaôen"
  56,52,"a ppeççem, war ccekk, si ttejôa n Zaqqum"
  56,53,A ppacaôem segs ifwaden
  56,54,"Sinna, a ppernum tissit seg waman iô$an"
  56,55,A ppetessem tissit ile$wman
  56,56,"D wagi ar asen d irsen, ass uqeîîi"
  56,57,D Nekwni ikwen Ixelqen. Lemmer a ppamnem
  56,58,Twalam l$ella id iteff$en segwen
  56,59,"D kunwi ip ixelqen, ne$ d Nekwni ay d ixellaqen"
  56,60,Nseyya tameppant garawen. Ur a£ izeggwir yiwen
  56,61,"iwakken a Nerr deg umkan nnwen wid i kwen icban; u kunwi, a kwen Nexleq d ayen ur tessinem"
  56,62,"Ni$ tesnem axlaq amenzu, lemmer tesmektayem"
  56,63,Twalam ayen tkerrzem
  56,64,"D kunwi i t ikerzen, ne$ d Nekwni ay d imekrazen"
  56,65,"Ma ihwa ya£, a t Nerr d uêvim, d$a a kwen tekkat lwehma"
  56,66,Aql a$ nepwalas
  56,67,"Sennig waya: aql a$ neppuêeôôem"
  56,68,Twalam aman i teppessem
  56,69,"D kunwi iten id isse$layen seg usigna, ne$ d Nekwni"
  56,70,"Ma ihwa ya£, a ten Nerr d imeô$anen. A lemmer tesnemmiren"
  56,71,Twalam times i tesskarem s uêukku
  56,72,"D kunwi i s d ixelqen ttjuô is, ne$ d Nekwni ay d Ixellaqen"
  56,73,"D Nekwni i p Irran d asmekti, u d lâafia i wid ineêwwaoen"
  56,74,"Sbuccaâ, s ccekôan, isem n Mass ik, Ameqwôaêan"
  56,75,"Ih, gulle$ seg wanda llan itran"
  56,76,"U, tagi, lemmer a ppeéôem, ard tagallit tameqwôaêant"
  56,77,Ar neppa d Leqwôan ukyis
  56,78,di Tezmamt iffren
  56,79,"Ur t pnalen, siwa wid zeddigen"
  56,80,D tarusi s$uô Mass imavalen
  56,81,"S usali agi, amendeô ma a ppiéidem"
  56,82,"S ôôeéq nnwen, kunwi tnekôem"
  56,83,Mara d tawev s agerjum
  56,84,"kunwi, imiren, teppaôoum"
  56,85,"Nekwni, sennig wen, i Neqôeb $uôes, maca, ur twalam ara"
  56,86,Xas ma ur tellim d wid ur nepwalas
  56,87,"erret p id, ma tessawalem tidep"
  56,88,Ma illa seg iqôiben
  56,89,"ihi, abeêri, laâîeô, di leonan n ssuâada"
  56,90,Ma illa seg iyeffusen
  56,91,"i keçç tifrat, seg iyeffusen"
  56,92,Ma illa seg inekkaôen innetlafen
  56,93,axxam is seg waman ippayzagen
  56,94,ad iô$ deg ujajiê
  56,95,"Ayagi, ih, d tidep itebbten"
  56,96,"Sbuccaâ, s ccekôan, isem n Mass ik Ameqwôaêan"
  57,1,"Sbuccuâen, s ccekôan Öebbi, ayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  57,2,"IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; Issidir, Ineqq; u Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  57,3,"D Neppa ay d amezwaru, ay d aneggaru; d ayen d ibanen akked wayen iffren. Neppa Iéôa yal cci"
  57,4,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, Iâannec af usgeld. Iéôa i ikeççmen ar tmurt, akked wayen id iteff$en segs, ayen id ippadren seg igenni, akked wayen ippalin $uôes. Neppa yidwen, anda ma tellam. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txedmem"
  57,5,IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ar Öebbi ara u$alen lumuô
  57,6,"Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren"
  57,7,"Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS! Efket seg wayen i$ef i kwen Irra, degs, d igensas. Wid iumnen segwen, iseddqen, d ameqwôan warraz nnsen"
  57,8,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tuminem ara s Öebbi? Amazan ipnabi kwen a ppamnem s Mass nnwen. Ni$ $uôes nnesba nnwen, ma tellam d lmumnin"
  57,9,"D Neppa id Issadren i umdan iS, issekniyen iberrzen, iwakken a kwen Issuffe$ si tillas ar tafat. Ih, Öebbi, fellawen, d Umâin Ipêunun"
  57,10,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tepseddiqem deg ubrid n Öebbi? N Öebbi lweôt n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur taâdilem ara: wid iseddqen uqbel l$elb, u nnu$en, widak, ad aâlayen, nezzeh, sennig wid iseddqen sin $er da, u nnu$en. Iwaââed asen akw Öebbi ûûam. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem"
  57,11,"Win iôevlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad as d Irr s lufa, u ines warraz ukyis"
  57,12,"Asmi ara twaliv lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, teddun tafat nnsen zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen: \"a lxiô nnwen, assa, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen a pwekkôem! D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan"
  57,13,"Ass ideg ixabiten, argaz tameîîut, ad inin i wid iumnen: \"arout a$, a neddem si tafat nnwen\"! A d inin: \"u$alet ar deffir, a d tqelbem tafat\"! Ad yili garasen lêiv, s tebburt. Zdaxel d aêunu, beôôa, zdat es: aâaqeb"
  57,14,"Ad sen d siwlen: \"day ur nella ara yidwen\"? Ad inin: \"ih! Maca, thewwlem iman nnwen, tekkukram, tcukkem, $elvent kwen lemcihwat, armi d iusa lameô n Öebbi. I$elv ikwen af Öebbi, u$ellav"
  57,15,"Assa, ur ipwaîîaf feddu segwen, ne$ seg wid ijehlen. Axxam nnwen d times; d neppat ay d bab nnwen. A tu$alin tucmip"
  57,16,"Âani maççi d lawan, i wid iumnen, ad rgagin wulawen nnsen ar usmekti n Öebbi, akked wayen id Issers n tidep? Ur ppilin am wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, zik, u tvul fellasen lmudda. D$a qquôen wulawen nnsen; aîas degsen d iballa$en"
  57,17,"Ecfut ar Öebbi Issidir tamurt, deffir tmeppant is. Ni$ Nbeggen awen d issekniyen, amendeô ma a pfehmem"
  57,18,"Ih, wid akked tid ipseddiqen, iôeîlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad asen d Irr s lufa, u nnsen arraz ukyis"
  57,19,"Wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS, d nitni ay d iêeqqiyen, u d inagan ar Mass nnsen. Ad awin arraz nnsen akked tafat nnsen. Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê"
  57,20,"Cfut ar tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan, d zzhu, d acebbeê, d zzux garawen, asuget n wayla akked derya. Am umedya ugeffur. Im$an is âaoben ijehliyen; sinna, ad isliwen, a ten twaliv ppiwôi$en; d$a ad êevmen. Di laxeôt, aâaqeb uqsiê akked ssmaê s$uô Öebbi, akked llza. Tameddurt n ddunit d zzehwa kan ip$uôôun"
  57,21,"£iwlet ar ssmaê n Mass nnwen, akked Loennet iwesâan am tmurt akked igenni, teppuhegga d i wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS. D wagi ay d lfevl n Öebbi. Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan"
  57,22,"Ur d tveôôu twa$it di tmurt, ne$ deg iman nnwen, siwa ma tura di Tezmamt, uqbel a p id Nawi. Ayagi, s tidep, d ayen isehlen i Öebbi"
  57,23,"Iwakken ur kwen ip$av wayen tzeglem, ur kwen issefôaê wayen i wen Ifka. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal amzuxi, imnefxi"
  57,24,"wid ipcuêêun, iêeppmen ccêa af medden. Win i iwexxôen…ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz"
  57,25,"Nuzen ed imazanen nne£, s ubeggen. Nessader ed yidsen Tazmamt akked lmizan, iwakken ad ddun imdanen s lêeqq. Nessader ed uzzal, degs vveôô uqsiê, akked uba$uô i medden, iwakken ad Iéeô Öebbi anwa ara ifken afus i Neppa akked imazanen iS, di tbavnit. Ih, Öebbi d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  57,26,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê akked Ibôahim. Nerra, si tarwa nnsen, Lambiyya, Tira. Degsen llan wid ipwanhan; aîas segsen d iballa$en"
  57,27,"Sinna, Nessevfeô ed, deffir sen, imazanen nne$. Nessevfeô ed Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Nefka yas Linoil. Nessekcem deg ulawen n wid iddan yides leênana akked tiéeî. Taxelwit, ur p Nuri fellasen; snulfan p id i llza n Öebbi. Ur qumen ara yis, akken iwata. Nefka arraz nnsen i wid iumnen segsen. Aîas, segsen, d iballa$en"
  57,28,"A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Amnet s Umazan iS. Ad awen Ifk sin imuren seg uêunu S, ad awen Irr tafat a ppeddum yis, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  57,29,"Akken ad éôen At Tezmamt, ar ur zmiren acemma di lfevl n Öebbi. Ih, lfevl deg ufus n Öebbi; Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan"